---
import { site } from '@/lib/site';
const { postsCount = 0 } = Astro.props;
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-copy">
    <p class="eyebrow">XIAONIGE · ASTRO BLOG</p>
    <h1>把复杂问题写清楚，把长期热爱留下来。</h1>
    <p class="hero-subtitle">一个更轻、更快、更安全的 GitHub Pages 博客发布器试点。</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a class="btn primary" href="#latest-posts">看最新文章</a>
      <a class="btn ghost" href="/archives/">浏览归档</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <aside class="poem-card">
    <span>今日诗词</span>
    <blockquote>“{site.poem.text}”</blockquote>
    <cite>—— {site.poem.from}</cite>
    <small>已迁移文章 {postsCount} 篇 · 音乐模块预留</small>
  </aside>
</section>
